'''4-羟基香豆素'''（{{lang-en|4-hydroxycoumarin}}）是一种[[香豆素|香豆素]][[衍生物|衍生物]]，和[[伞形花内酯|伞形花内酯]]（7-羟基香豆素）为[[同分异构体|同分异构体]]，其[[羟基|羟基]]位置为4号位，发现于[[草木犀属|草木犀属]]（学名：''Melilotus''）植物<ref>{{cite journal | author = Bye, A. | author2 = King, H. K. | date = 1970 | title = The biosynthesis of 4-hydroxycoumarin and dicoumarol by Aspergillus fumigatus Fresenius | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_biochemical-journal_1970-04_117_2/page/237 | journal = Biochemical Journal | volume = 117 | issue = 2 | pages = 237–245| pmid = 4192639 | pmc = 1178855 | doi=10.1042/bj1170237}}</ref>。

